# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS
http://kabirsantsharan.com/* https://kabirsantsharan.com/:splat 301!
http://www.kabirsantsharan.com/* https://kabirsantsharan.com/:splat 301!

# Redirect www to non-www (if using custom domain)
https://www.kabirsantsharan.com/* https://kabirsantsharan.com/:splat 301!

# SPA fallback - ensure all routes go to index.html for client-side routing
/* /index.html 200

# API routes (if you add them later)
/api/* /api/:splat 200

# Legacy redirects (if migrating from old site)
/about-kabir /teachings 301
/satsang /events 301
/blog/* /teachings/:splat 301